PrecisRegulations Amending the YUKON TERRITORY FISHERY REGULATIONS by eliminating some restrictions on the issuance of Yukon River Salmon Licences, by establishing separate close times for the commercial and domestic salmon fisheries on the Yukon River and its tributaries, and by clarifying that the restriction concerning the use of single-pointed barbless hooks only applies during the salmon spawning season (July 1 to October 15).
